{"tid":1531211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【機場月】907 繼續交通壓力測試  908繼續遊行集會？","createTime":"2019-09-02T06:56:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T05:40:03.000Z","uid":124134,"like":31,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"5365c12694c270a628b4900b5f0aed6b61ccf7cf","tid":1531211,"uid":124134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T06:56:02.000Z","msg":"見好多人都唔知今個weekend有咩做<br />\n<br />\n小弟建議907再做真&bull;壓力測試（之前都有人提過9月係機場月）<br />\n尋日901個壓力測試不完美，要改善，但唔可以放棄春袋<br />\n尋日好多人塞車塞到入東涌就要走，連袋皮都未掂到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n907測試開始時間可提早到11點開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n目標係要入到機場巴士總站等車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而唔係東涌  亦都唔係暢航路/國泰城<br />\n<br />\n而星期日908就做番遊行/集會譴責濫權濫捕<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">港共就係睇死我地玩到開學就收皮<br />\n唔係要輸比佢地睇呀？<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n以下附一張圖，睇下尋晚19:11機場巴士站情況，無防暴無速龍，其實<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>機場愈近客運大樓愈安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span> credit to 機場 Fact Check 資訊頻道<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tKXVw6y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtKXVw6y.jpg&h=ace43019&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有其他更好planning<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"27a2b1158bb9cd64063d7d0683b5dd18d8fecc94","tid":1531211,"uid":124134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T06:57:11.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"4c083aced193b043db41e924ae99fcc4d11857cc","tid":1531211,"uid":124134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T06:57:21.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"5b9d2088dad94440faed85